This is the beginnings of a tiny utility library for working with HBase in the REPL.

Do not feed the bears.

shared shared shared, shared nothing

Author: Kyle Oba ;; mudphone ;; kyleoba <@> gmail.com
---------------------- -- -- -- - - ---- -- - -- -- --- -- - -- --- - - -- -- - - - -

Some notes:
- This currently works with HBase 0.20.0 and as such the HBase 0.20.0 jar must be on 
  your classpath.

...... .  . ..... .. .. . .. .................................. ... .... .. ... . ...
Instructions for use... While in the REPL...

Either do this:
> (require 'mudphone.hbase-runner.repl-cheat)
> (in-ns 'mudphone.hbase-runner.repl-cheat) 
> (list-tables)

Or, do this:
> (use 'mudphone.hbase-runner.repl-cheat)
> (list-tables)

Enjoy!